videos.description: Storm Murphy drops off a pass to Chevez Goodwin who goes up to hammer down a powerful dunk with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wofford's Murphy sets up Goodwin for emphatic slam) 2020/03/09

videos.headline: Wofford's Murphy sets up Goodwin for emphatic slam

videos.description: Chevez Goodwin rises up to swat down the ETSU layup attempt, then Tray Hollowell secures the rebound and runs the break to score a quick transition layup.

videos.headline: Goodwin's monster block sets up Hollowell's bucket

videos.description: Storm Murphy splashes a 3-pointer for Wofford, then Isaiah Tisdale immediately answers by crossing his defender over and draining a 3-pointer of his own.
videos.headline: Tisdale crosses defender, splashes 3-pointer
